      {According to the monitoring, Daniel's speed in the fourth passage slowed down significantly, and his breathing rate also decreased. In addition, a red gas of a certain composition filled the passage. An office worker who happened to pass by during this period was later questioned and found that he felt obvious weakness when passing through the fourth passage, but it is not clear whether it was caused by the gas. 
Daniel's physical condition obviously deteriorated in the gas. After he stopped, a rabbit with a bright red body and a short tail appeared in the corner of the monitoring screen. Its file was supplemented in the subsequent investigation.}
